    workedExample: "Triton GEMM for M=N=K=4096, BLOCK_M=BLOCK_N=128, BLOCK_K=64: grid = (M//128, N//128) = (32, 32) programs. Each program does K/64=64 iterations of tl.dot. Total: 32×32×64 = 65,536 tile dot products of shape 128×64×128.",
