    computation: "Softmax row: row = tl.load(...); row_max = tl.max(row, axis=0); row -= row_max; row_exp = tl.exp(row); row_sum = tl.sum(row_exp, axis=0); result = row_exp / row_sum. All operations are on tile; only 2 global loads and 1 store.",
