    workedExample: "Without tiling: 4096² output elements, each reading 4096+4096 floats = 4096³×2 reads = 137 GB. With TILE=128: reads = M/128 × N/128 × 2 × 128² loads per tile × K/128 K-tiles = 4096³×2 / 128 × 2 = 1.07 GB. 128× fewer global reads.",
